OL,6,FA mother charged of murdering her son
OL,7,Fhas also been accused of attempting to
OL,8,Fmurder her own father, a court has
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FKarolina Zurawska, from Gendros,
OL,12,FSwansea, appeared at Swansea Crown
OL,13,FCourt on Tuesday morning.
OL,15,FThe 41-year-old is charged with
OL,16,Fmurdering her six-year-old son
OL,17,FAlexander Zurawski, who was found dead
OL,18,Fat a property in Cwm Du Close, Gendros
OL,19,Fon Thursday 29 August.
