OL,6,FShe is also accused of attempting to
OL,7,Fmurder her father, Krzysztof Siwi, 67,
OL,8,Fearlier the same day.
OL,10,FDuring a short hearing, Zurawska spoke
OL,11,Fonly to confirm her name and that she
OL,12,Fcould hear the proceedings.
OL,14,FThe defendant, who appeared via video-
OL,15,Flink from prison, did not enter a plea
OL,16,Ffor the two charges against her.
OL,18,FThe trial will take place on February
OL,19,F17 next year and is expected to last
OL,20,Fbetween 1 and 2 weeks.
