OL,6,FAlexander's family described him in a
OL,7,Fstatement issued by South Wales Police
OL,8,Fas a "very kind child".
OL,10,F"He loved playing with his little
OL,11,Fsister and playing with his dog,
OL,12,FDaisy," they said.
OL,14,FThe family thanked the emergency
OL,15,Fservices who were involved in the
OL,16,Fincident last Thursday.
