OL,6,FBethan Peterson, headteacher of
OL,7,FWhitestone Primary School, said:
OL,8,F"Alexander was a delightful,
OL,9,Fdetermined little boy whose tenacity
OL,10,Fand positive demeanour ensured his
OL,11,Fsuccess in all he undertook.
OL,13,F"He was an extremely loved and popular
OL,14,Fboy amongst his peers, staff and with
OL,15,Fall who knew him. He will be sadly
OL,16,Fmissed."
